> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/pageshow_event\"><code>pageshow</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/paste_event\"><code>paste</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/popstate_event\"><code>popstate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/rejectionhandled_event\"><code>rejectionhandled</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/storage_event\"><code>storage</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/unhandledrejection_event\"><code>unhandledrejection</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/unload_event\"><code>unload</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplayactivate_event\"><code>vrdisplayactivate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplayblur_event\"><code>vrdisplayblur</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplayconnect_event\"><code>vrdisplayconnect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaydeactivate_event\"><code>vrdisplaydeactivate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaydisconnect_event\"><code>vrdisplaydisconnect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplayfocus_event\"><code>vrdisplayfocus</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypointerrestricted_event\"><code>vrdisplaypointerrestricted</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypointerunrestricted_event\"><code>vrdisplaypointerunrestricted</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypresentchange_event\"><code>vrdisplaypresentchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"podsumowanie","title":"Podsumowanie","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Zwraca obiekt zaznaczenia reprezentujący zakres tekstu zaznaczonego przez użytkownika. Zauważ, że nie ma to żadnego powiązania z obiektem listy selekcji DOM!</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sk.c5.82adnia","title":"Składnia","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\"><i>selection</i> =<i>window</i>.getSelection();\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parametry","title":"Parametry","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code>selection</code> jest obiektem <a href=\"pl/DOM/Selection\">selekcji</a>.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ad","title":"Przykład","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">function foo() {\n   var selObj = window.getSelection();\n   alert(selObj);\n   var selRange = selObj.getRangeAt(0);\n   // teraz możemy operować na zakresie\n}\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"uwagi","title":"Uwagi","isH3":true,"content":"<p>W JavaScript, kiedy przesyłany jest obiekt selekcji do funkcji, zamiast jej, przesyłana jest jej reprezentacja w postaci ciągu znaków (tj. zaznaczony tekst). Może to złudnie przypominać, że obiekt selekcji wygląda jak ciąg znaków (obiekt <code>string</code>), kiedy tak naprawdę ma swoje własne właściwości i metody. Dokładniej, zwracana jest wartość wywołania metody <code><a href=\"pl/DOM/Selection/toString\">toString()</a></code>. <span class=\"comment\">I'm treading carefully with the word \"convert\" here because it could be misinterpreted as a permanent convert - Maian</span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specyfikacja","title":"Specyfikacja","isH3":true,"content":"<p>DOM poziomu 0. Nie jest częścią specyfikacji.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"zobacz_r.c3.b3wnie.c5.bc","title":"Zobacz również","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code><a href=\"pl/DOM/Selection\">Selection</a>, <a href=\"pl/DOM/range\">Range</a></code></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"noinclude\" id=\"sect1\">\n &nbsp;</div>\n<p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Zwraca obiekt zaznaczenia reprezentujący zakres tekstu zaznaczonego przez użytkownika. Zauważ, że nie ma to żadnego powiązania z obiektem listy selekcji DOM!","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Window.getSelection()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"window.getSelection","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"window.getSelection","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"window.getSelection","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Window.getSelection()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Window.getSelection()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Window.getSelection()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Window.getSelection","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/api/window/getselection","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/api/window/getselection/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API","title":"Lista Web API"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/Window","title":"window"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/Window/getSelection","title":"window.getSelection"}],"pageTitle":"window.getSelection - Lista Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}